            "usecases": "AI collaboration with human oversight, AI for problem-solving collaboration, Act as a co-pilot for work tasks, Chunked interaction with AI, Client-driven AI workflow adaptation, Co-pilot workflow with human control, Collaborate on document creation, Collaborate with colleague on AI tool testing, Collaborative AI task execution, Collaborative AI workflow, Collaborative AI workflow, Collaborative AI workflow, Collaborative human-AI workflow, Collaborative policy drafting, Collaborative refinement of AI outputs, Collaborative task completion with AI, Collaborative task refinement with AI, Collaborative task refinement with AI, Collaborative task workflow, Collaborative workflow partner, Collaborative, iterative AI interaction, Context management across AI conversations, Develop remote team activities, Enable voice-based AI collaboration, Filtering AI suggestions through interpersonal insight, Human-AI collaboration for financial safety, Human-AI collaborative problem solving, Human-in-the-loop AI collaboration, Improve workflow efficiency through AI collaboration, Manage multiple AI tools as a team, Ongoing AI collaboration during development, Real-time AI assistance on-site, Rehearse police interaction scenarios, Replicating office collaboration with AI, Sharing AI-assisted work with colleagues, Speaker diarization with human oversight, Step-by-step AI collaboration with agents, Step-by-step project assistance via conversational AI, Step-by-step task collaboration, Structured AI conversation workflows, Supervised AI workflow design, Support collaborative test planning, Troubleshooting partner during project execution"
